Trudy Ekspeditsii Imperatorskago Russkago Geograficheskago Obshchestva, Sovershennoi v

description.@value: コズロフが、1899～1901年にかけてアルタイ山脈、ゴビ経由でチベットに入り、黄河源を調査した時の報告書。Vol.3。

Kozlov is one of three successors to Przheval'skii. This is a report of his expedition from 1899 to 1901, when he entered Tibet via the Altai Mountains and Gobi to study the origin of the Yellow River.
